dct_description_sm: From the latest Netherlands Government surveys ; published Jan. 1917 at the Hydrographic Office, under the authority of the Secretary of the Navy.
Depths shown by soundings; relief by form lines and spot heights.
Navigational lines, "Streams & Currents" note, Tidal Information chart.
Shows low water, reefs, waterways, roads, railroads, islands.
